Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maurer, you haven't been\Ntaking a bath, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.84,0:00:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised, when I moved\Nto the desk next to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'd take one every other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a visitor\Nin the reception office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home,\Nso make your own tea, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A visitor? At this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't had a bath, either.\NHe smells almost as bad as you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell...?\NUpsy daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And whose fault is it that\NI haven't been able to take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't realize that she's able to\Nmake a living at this paper
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,with no future,\Nthanks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... My name is Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask for your assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... He really is filthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so you're a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, Doctor,\Nis this what you're trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The next target of the person\Nwho's been Killing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,middle-aged couples\Nthroughout Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is here in Heidelberg?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That couple is fostering a young girl,\Nand when that girl turns 20,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.95,0:01:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the killer will come to take her away...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he does, the foster parents\Nare sure to be Killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have no idea\Nwho that girl or her foster parents are,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,or where they live...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's not delusional,\NI don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a joke. Please believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous! Not even the gossip rags\Nwould write up that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here\Nto get you to write it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:02:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,After those twins\Nslipped out of the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there is at least\Na 6-month blank period
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,before the brother showed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that,\Nafter leaving the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,those twins came to\NHeidelberg together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And the two were raised by\Nthe girl's current foster parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But the brother ran away from here\Nafter a short period,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving his sister behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you write a novel?\N'Course it probably won't sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible that there is\Na missing person's report out on the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And there might even be\Na newspaper article about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me check the newspapers\Nfrom nine years ago! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't allow\Nany more people to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The president has a thing against\Ncomputerization, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,These are smaller versions\Nof the daily newspapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and manuscript files.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are files\Nof cancelled stories and raw data.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the Japanese bow...?\NYou're quite welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't have the time\Nto spend on silly stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and leave\Nwhen you're satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Every once in a while,\NI get a nut case like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.19,Monster - Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.59,Monster - Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Please let me find something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:23.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(362,350)\fad(686,835)}The Missing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.\NYou're looking well, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fainting like that...\NYou startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you really didn't like\Nthe boy we hooked you up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I just suddenly felt bad.\NI have to apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind.\NYou don't have to worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That Otto... When I talked to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out that he's not\Nyour “prince on a white horse.”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he didn't send you\Nany email message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that you fainted\Nbecause you saw that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I only saw him for a second,\Nso I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your impression of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt very nostalgic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not it...\NI can't explain it well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You needn't force yourself, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to put it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it felt just like\Nwhen I had that nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute evil”...\NIt's beginning to sound religious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't go to a church...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it seems to me that\Neverything will be cleared up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,if I see that person again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel that you will regain\Nthe memory you've lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one means you may be\Nable to employ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think you should let that\Nbe a burden on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about your future\Nwithout stressing, is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Just work up a sweat\Nplaying sports,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and your insecurities\Nshould disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maurer, pull another all-nighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, were you the one\Nwho let that guy use the file room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I asked him\Nwhat he was doing there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and he said\Nyou had given him permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean he's still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! It's about time you... Huh'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Hey! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, isn't it?\NI always have breakfast here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you go home?\NWhat about your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't got one.\NMy wife left me, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always so busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When I finally realized it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,my wife had gone back to her parents\Nwith our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever thought about\Nbringing your wife home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who walked out!\NWhy should I go to get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you seem to regret\Nbeing so occupied with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Work is most important to a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Any wife who cannot understand that\Nis welcome to leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It was none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NIt's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... One more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You smoke too much.\NI say that as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit saying the same thing\Nmy wife said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife was worried\Nabout your health, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina's birthday present?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I finally finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Her sweaters used to be\Nthis tiny before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, are you really going to tell her\Nthat she's not really our daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't we leave it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...\NThere's no need to tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina is our daughter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy... am I hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about the future...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gaitel may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:11:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow, your birthday, let's meet at\NHeidelberg Castle at 7:00 PM."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow... at Heidelberg Castle...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so busy, but here I am staring at\Na mountain of papers with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time you gave up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If... it's just a thought, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to go to get my wife...\NDo you think she'd come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If you quit smoking, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,11-year-old boy disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible that he was kidnapped,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but there has been no word\Nfrom a kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,16 Necker Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone named Fortner has filled out\Na missing person's report!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The raw data should be\Nin here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that that killer would
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,come to take his sister away\Nwhen she turned 20, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If the boy in this article\Nis her brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! His birth date is printed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the 20th birthday\Nof those twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hello, Dad? It's me.\NI just finished work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to meet up with a friend\Nthen I'll be coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... At Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:13:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom is making preparations\Nfor a birthday party, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She says she's going to meet\Na friend before coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina's all grown up, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:17.75,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,Maybe this will help me\Nto remember things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:25.73,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,I want to know who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, what do you intend to do if\Nthe twin girl is at the Fortners' home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case,\Nthat family is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I will contact the police\Nand ask for protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the police will\Ndo anything just from your reasoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has happened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be too late\Nafter something happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's going to happen.\NIt's all in your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Doctor...\NOf the four murder cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself went to\Nthe crime scene in Cologne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something different\Nabout that scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I sensed no purpose,\Nno greed, no bitterness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like someone simply ended\Nthese people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell just by looking\Nat the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that a kid\Nwho wasn't even 20, did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you think a youngster could
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,kill those people\Nwithout feeling any emotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't something done by a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bigger... What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't find the right words\Nto describe this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have to describe it, it's trite,\Nbut that was the Devil's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If that killer were to appear before me,\NI would Kill him without a pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,16 Necker Street... We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!\NSorry to call on you so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to bother you.\NI'm Maurer of the Heidelberg Post.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What would a newspaper reporter\Nbe wanting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'd like to ask you\Nsome questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?\N— Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's regarding this missing persons report\Nthat you filed in 1986...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can forget about that matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Could you please talk to us?\NDon't you have a girl living with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The twin sister of\Nthe boy who disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They had a birthday cake prepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You took in a pair of twins\Nnine years ago, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl still lives with you,\Ndoesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We have raised her\Nas our true daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't make waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You took in a pair of twins\Nnine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy had surgical scars\Non his head
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the girl had amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fortner, you must contact\Nthe police at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lives, and your daughter's,\Nare in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let us see your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She is out at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she was going\Nto meet a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me use your car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! We must\Nnotify the police first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the time\Nto explain things to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the key, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll call them from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful! As I said earlier,\Nhe's a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back alive...\NThen I'll quit smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow the quack's advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife will be happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how should I explain\Nthis to the police...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our daughter... Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NLet me use your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened to our daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone line's been cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... Please be safe... Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way past time...\NI guess that message was a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to... wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asked to make sure\Nyou waited here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to wait...\NDon't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was told!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... No, you're Nina Fortner,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?\NI'm Dr. Tenma. I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. You must go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You... Are you...\Nmy prince on a white horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't butt in... Don't butt in, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gotta wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't, I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He said no one would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm amazed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I need something to tie him up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:20:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who asked you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When did he say he was coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He just said\Nhe would come here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,after doing something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... your home...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to hurry back to your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later!\NWe've got to hurry, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna...\N—Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... I can't get loose...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:22:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me! Who are you?\NAnd I'm not Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, when you were brought into\Nmy hospital, you were Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And your brother's name was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
